title: Terry Goodkind - Sword of Truth series
description:
The entire Sword of Truth series! they are iphone, ipod touch, and ipad compatible! 

I put another book in here from Terry Goodkind call "The Law of Nines" it is not with the Sword of Truth series but it is a great book. =]

I hope you all enjoy this series!

To get them all on itunes just follow these instructions:
1: open up itunes
2: click on "File"
3: then on the drop down menu click "Add Folder" and navigate itunes to the folder with the series.
4: click "open"

then you are set to put them on your iDevice of your choice. =]
